Package menuapp.Pages

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AddMenuItemPage
    The AddMenuItemPage class represents a page in the application where users can add new menu items.
    AddStaffPage
    The AddStaffPage class represents a page in the application where users can add new staff members.
    AdminPage
    The AdminPage class implements the IPage interface and represents the administration management console within the application.
    BranchManagerOptionsPage
    The BranchManagerOptionsPage class implements the IPage interface and serves as the main interface for branch managers within the application.
    CustOrderPage
    The CustOrderPage class implements the IPage interface and facilitates the entire ordering process for customers.
    EditMenuItemPage
    The EditMenuItemPage class implements the IPage interface and provides functionalities to edit existing menu items.
    ManagerOptionsPage
    The ManagerOptionsPage class implements the IPage interface and acts as a controller within the application, facilitating the management of menu items and staff details for branch managers.
    RemoveMenuItemPage
    The RemoveMenuItemPage class implements the IPage interface and is responsible for removing a menu item from the system's menu list.
    RemoveStaffPage
    The RemoveStaffPage class implements the IPage interface, providing functionalities to remove staff members from a system.
    StaffLoginPage
    The StaffLoginPage class implements the IPage interface and facilitates the staff login process for the application.
    TransferStaffPage
    The TransferStaffPage class implements the IPage interface and provides functionality for transferring staff members between different branches or departments within the organization.
